title: 17. Job Versatility And What You Can Do With Your Esthetician License
description:
Hey everyone! In today's episode we are diving even deeper into what you can do with your esthetician license, from makeup to sales to education and more. Let us know what you think and where you've landed in your career - are you in the spa or in a different role? Xo, Tess and Lo

Tess' Instagram @myestytessa.dermaplus + Tess' YouTube: Tess Zolly 

Lauren's Instagram: @laurens.esthetics 

Music by LiQwYd
